Each day Donald Trump continues to spew false claims of fraud he is undermining our country and system of government. It is past time for my Republican colleagues to publicly recognize Joe Biden as President-elect and push Trump to do the same. Today now -- do the right thing.

Congratulations to President-elect Joe Biden and Vice President-elect Kamala Harris and to the American people for the historic level of participation in this critical election.  Ready to get to work to build America back better.    Onwards!
Good news for America! https://t.co/pwCFAe1wB9

Almost there! Restoring leadership and sanity to the White House.  @JoeBiden "The purpose of our politics the work of the nation isn't to fan the flames of conflict but solve problems. To guarantee justice. To give everybody a fair shot. And to improve the lives of our people"
Despicable. Trump used White House podium tonight to spew his completely false narrative about the election and our democracy. Fact checkers searching for one truthful word in tonight's remarks...
Always their plan -- never thought they'd actually say it out loud. https://t.co/11NyjZMlzQ
GOP senators are still cowering before Trump. It’s long past time they stand up for our democracy and call upon Trump to stop his fraudulent attacks on counting the ballots.

I am confident that when all the votes in the battleground states are counted Joe Biden will be our next president and Kamala Harris our next vice-president. Every American regardless of party should agree that every ballot must be counted and every voice heard.

I want to salute voters across Maryland for voting in large numbers and congratulations to the Maryland candidates who were elected. I look forward to working with all Marylanders as we continue to move our state forward.

The lines may be long but Maryland Voters are energized! Pleased to join Prince George's County State's Attorney @SABraveboy at the polls in Fort Washington for Joe and Kamala! https://t.co/tZKpyaGsmW
